Setup:
$ mkdir -p ~/.config/awesome
$ ln -s ${DOTFILES}/awesome/rc.lua ~/.config/awesome/rc.lua
$ ln -s ${DOTFILES}/awesome/theme.lua ~/.config/awesome/theme.lua

My config also uses several widgets:
  - network-manager-applet:
    install: changes based on distro
    widgets:
      * Network widget

  - awesome-wm-widgets:
    URL: https://pavelmakhov.com/awesome-wm-widgets
    install: $ git clone https://github.com/streetturtle/awesome-wm-widgets ~/.config/awesome/awesome-wm-widgets
    widgets:
      * Battery widget
      * Brightness widget
      * Volume widget
